11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14void
15printifname(format, name, ifp)
16 char *format, *name;
17 void *ifp;
18{
19 PRINTF("%s%s", format, name);
20 if ((ifp == NULL) && strcmp(name, "-") && strcmp(name, "*"))
21 PRINTF("(!)");
22}
